00:27:10.260 --> 00:27:11.759
y casi te pierdo.

00:27:14.359 --> 00:27:15.720
Me arrepentí al instante.

00:27:16.359 --> 00:27:17.720
Pensé que era tal

00:27:18.559 --> 00:27:19.720
